data.description: Great investment opportunity or first home! This 3 bed, 2 bath home is located in the heart of Converse! Placed perfectly in a cul de sac and neighborhood has no HOA! Large living area with plenty of natural light including a fireplace! Kitchen offers ample counter space, generous lot complete with a covered patio that makes it perfect for entertaining! Minutes away from I-35, shopping and the Forum!
